OL,3,CFrom Wakefield under-10s to Wembley:
OL,4,CCup final ref's 'nerves'
OL,6,FMadley, 40, said: "To get that phone
OL,7,Fcall to say that you're going to be
OL,8,Frefereeing this year's FA Cup final,
OL,9,Fthat's the dream, that's the pinnacle
OL,10,Fwhen you become a referee. I watched
OL,11,Fthe game from being seven or eight
OL,12,Fyears old and you'd sit in front of
OL,13,Fthe television and you wouldn't move
OL,14,Fall day.
OL,16,F"I think there'll be a mixture of
OL,17,Fexcitement and nerves but hopefully
OL,18,Fthey'll all pull together and help me
OL,19,Fand my team perform well on the day."
