OL,3,CFrom Wakefield under-10s to Wembley:
OL,4,CCup final ref's 'nerves'
OL,6,FAlthough he is now one of the UK's top
OL,7,Freferees, Madley admits he wasn't
OL,8,Fenamoured with the job to start with.
OL,10,FHe said: "Being perfectly honest, the
OL,11,Ffirst two years I questioned whether
OL,12,Fit was for me. I did it because it
OL,13,Fprobably put a little bit of petrol in
OL,14,Fthe car and paid for the odd beer in
OL,15,Fthe student union while I was at
OL,16,Funiversity.
