OL,3,CFrom Wakefield under-10s to Wembley:
OL,4,CCup final ref's 'nerves'
OL,6,FAndy Madley said: "He'd seen me be an
OL,7,Fassistant referee in the Premier
OL,8,FLeague, he'd never seen me referee a
OL,9,FFootball League game.
OL,11,F"But also one of the songs that we
OL,12,Fplayed at his funeral was Abide With
OL,13,FMe, which obviously gets played at the
OL,14,FFA Cup final so I think that'll be
OL,15,Fquite a touching moment, I hope the
OL,16,Fcameras aren't on me at that point."
